00:26:48,994 --> 00:26:50,234
- It's peaceful.
- Yes.

766
00:26:50,834 --> 00:26:51,933
That's a great way to put it.

767
00:26:51,934 --> 00:26:53,803
- It's like we're covered in clouds.
- Well...

768
00:26:53,804 --> 00:26:55,303
The best way to end today's trip...

769
00:26:55,304 --> 00:26:57,273
would be a cozy place to sleep, right?

770
00:26:57,274 --> 00:26:59,080
- That would be the best.
- That'd be the icing on the cake.

771
00:26:59,104 --> 00:27:00,573
- Everyone, - Seriously.

772
00:27:00,574 --> 00:27:03,213
A chance to sleep in the traditional hanok house is at stake...

773
00:27:03,214 --> 00:27:04,894
on tonight's Sleeping Indoors or Outdoors.

774
00:27:05,184 --> 00:27:06,754
It's called Track Yakult.

775
00:27:06,814 --> 00:27:08,084
- What?
- Track Yakult?

776
00:27:09,054 --> 00:27:10,883
- Track Yakult.
- What's Track Yakult?

777
00:27:10,884 --> 00:27:12,623
Listen up. You will each receive...

778
00:27:12,624 --> 00:27:14,693
- two mini bottles of yogurt drink.
- Okay.

779
00:27:14,694 --> 00:27:17,223
Each bottle will have one syllable of your name.

780
00:27:17,224 --> 00:27:19,164
- Like "Jong" and "Min."
- Okay. I see.

781
00:27:19,424 --> 00:27:21,933
(You must drink it up to see the letters.)

782
00:27:21,934 --> 00:27:23,703
You will each take turns...

783
00:27:23,704 --> 00:27:27,374
to hide two mini bottles that have your names on them.

784
00:27:27,574 --> 00:27:28,904
What's the boundary?

785
00:27:29,004 --> 00:27:31,684
(Their current location, the area where they can't hide the drinks)

786
00:27:31,744 --> 00:27:34,943
(The area where they can hide the drinks)

787
00:27:34,944 --> 00:27:36,273
(Backyard, small room, main room, )

788
00:27:36,274 --> 00:27:37,954
(box room, front yard, TV room, side yard)

789
00:27:38,144 --> 00:27:42,584
(Front yard)

790
00:27:43,214 --> 00:27:46,554
(Side yard)

791
00:27:47,094 --> 00:27:50,594
(Backyard)

792
00:27:50,994 --> 00:27:53,864
(TV room)

793
00:27:54,264 --> 00:27:57,334
(Main room)

794
00:27:58,104 --> 00:28:00,634
(Small room)

795
00:28:01,334 --> 00:28:04,744
(Box room)

796
00:28:05,274 --> 00:28:08,743
(The entire living quarters are their mission zone.)

797
00:28:08,744 --> 00:28:11,414
Once all of you hide your drinks,

798
00:28:11,644 --> 00:28:13,183
the real mission will begin.

799
00:28:13,184 --> 00:28:14,213
- Do we have to find them?
- Yes.

800
00:28:14,214 --> 00:28:15,883
You will be given 15 minutes...

801
00:28:15,884 --> 00:28:18,723
to find other members' yogurt drinks and drink them.

802
00:28:18,724 --> 00:28:19,724
Once you do,

803
00:28:19,725 --> 00:28:20,923
- you can submit the bottles.
- We have to drink them?

804
00:28:20,924 --> 00:28:22,693
- We have to complete their names?
- That's right.

805
00:28:22,694 --> 00:28:24,323
- Let's say I only found "Jong."
- Okay.

806
00:28:24,324 --> 00:28:26,263
- Can I bring it over to you first?
- Right.

807
00:28:26,264 --> 00:28:27,633
- Yes.
- If I find "Min" and drink it,

808
00:28:27,634 --> 00:28:29,094
- Okay.
- then Jong Min is out.

809
00:28:29,364 --> 00:28:31,203
What if you only find "Jong" and can't find "Min?"

810
00:28:31,204 --> 00:28:32,233
Then he's not eliminated yet?

811
00:28:32,234 --> 00:28:33,773
That person will still be in the game.

812
00:28:33,774 --> 00:28:35,133
As soon as your name is submitted,

813
00:28:35,134 --> 00:28:37,343
outdoor sleeping is confirmed.

814
00:28:37,344 --> 00:28:38,374
- Okay.
- I see.

815
00:28:38,874 --> 00:28:41,173
- How many people?
- A total of three members...

816
00:28:41,174 --> 00:28:42,474
will sleep outdoors tonight.

817
00:28:42,814 --> 00:28:43,814
That's a lot.

818
00:28:44,484 --> 00:28:46,084
- Listen carefully from now on.
- Okay.

819
00:28:46,384 --> 00:28:48,183
Within 15 minutes,

820
00:28:48,184 --> 00:28:49,883
if three outdoor sleepers...

821
00:28:49,884 --> 00:28:51,283
- If they aren't determined?
- aren't determined...

822
00:28:51,284 --> 00:28:52,453
- Yes?
- Will everyone sleep indoors?

823
00:28:52,454 --> 00:28:54,094
- Everyone will sleep outdoors.
- Oh, my.

824
00:28:54,494 --> 00:28:55,654
That's the worst.

825
00:28:55,794 --> 00:28:57,163
- Do we have to find three people?
- Yes.

826
00:28:57,164 --> 00:28:58,493
- If not...
- If we don't eliminate three,

827
00:28:58,494 --> 00:28:59,793
- will all of us be eliminated?
- Yes.

828
00:28:59,794 --> 00:29:01,133
- That's correct.
- We must be careful about that.

829
00:29:01,134 --> 00:29:03,704
However, you may not possess Yakult bottles...

830
00:29:03,904 --> 00:29:05,263
with your name on it.

831
00:29:05,264 --> 00:29:07,573
If you get eliminated, the bottles...

832
00:29:07,574 --> 00:29:08,934
you have will be submitted.

833
00:29:09,104 --> 00:29:11,904
As you can see, the order will be important.

834
00:29:12,104 --> 00:29:13,374
- The order of hiding?
- Yes.

835
00:29:14,114 --> 00:29:15,114
All right.

836
00:29:15,115 --> 00:29:16,643
(Let's decide by drawing spoons.)

837
00:29:16,644 --> 00:29:18,643
- DinDin goes first.
- DinDin, Se Yoon,

838
00:29:18,644 --> 00:29:20,630
- Going first may not be good.
- Joon, Seon Ho, Jong Min.

839
00:29:20,654 --> 00:29:22,254
All right, number one.

840
00:29:22,684 --> 00:29:24,754
- DinDin, please start.
- Okay.

841
00:29:24,854 --> 00:29:26,083
- All right.
- Where are his Yakult bottles?

842
00:29:26,084 --> 00:29:27,204
Will he get them over there?

843
00:29:27,894 --> 00:29:30,363
Let's try to predict where DinDin would go.

844
00:29:30,364 --> 00:29:33,634
I'm going to put them right in the front.

845
00:29:33,894 --> 00:29:35,564
- Okay.
- He would definitely do that.

846
00:29:35,664 --> 00:29:37,633
Can we take as long as we want to hide them?

847
00:29:37,634 --> 00:29:39,164
- Right now...
- Won't we get a lot?

848
00:29:39,504 --> 00:29:41,833
Listen to me carefully.

849
00:29:41,834 --> 00:29:43,273
I'm not saying this because he isn't here.

850
00:29:43,274 --> 00:29:44,873
(He starts to talk about DinDin behind his back.)

851
00:29:44,874 --> 00:29:47,874
Seriously, when DinDin left,

852
00:29:48,514 --> 00:29:50,914
- he wasn't worried at all.
- Right.

853
00:29:51,284 --> 00:29:52,964
- I really can't stand that.
- Me neither.

854
00:29:53,344 --> 00:29:55,113
- "When we play games like this,"
- It's a given.

855
00:29:55,114 --> 00:29:56,313
- "I'll definitely sleep indoors."
- Exactly.

856
00:29:56,314 --> 00:29:57,953
- He looks down on us.
- You could...

857
00:29:57,954 --> 00:29:59,253
feel confident about it.

858
00:29:59,254 --> 00:30:01,894
He didn't show his willingness to try hard.

859
00:30:02,694 --> 00:30:04,894
"I'll just put them here."

860
00:30:05,424 --> 00:30:06,723
- You're right.
- He was at ease.

861
00:30:06,724 --> 00:30:08,063
(He acts arrogant from start to finish.)

862
00:30:08,064 --> 00:30:09,193
- This is what I can't stand.
- He's so annoying.

863
00:30:09,194 --> 00:30:12,033
Is DinDin statistically more likely to survive...

864
00:30:12,034 --> 00:30:13,633
in a game like this?

865
00:30:13,634 --> 00:30:14,734
- He's good.
- Yes, he is.

866
00:30:14,974 --> 00:30:16,004
- And?
- And so...

867
00:30:16,634 --> 00:30:18,074
Let me propose this before we start.

868
00:30:18,244 --> 00:30:19,244
That sounds good.

869
00:30:19,245 --> 00:30:20,813
- Here's my suggestion.
- That's not bad.

870
00:30:20,814 --> 00:30:21,944
This is a rebellion.

871
00:30:22,314 --> 00:30:23,813
DinDin went first.

872
00:30:23,814 --> 00:30:24,943
(As soon as we find DinDin's Yakult)

873
00:30:24,944 --> 00:30:27,253
If one of us finds his,

874
00:30:27,254 --> 00:30:28,553
- I found number one?
- we should give a sign.

875
00:30:28,554 --> 00:30:29,913
If I find one...

876
00:30:29,914 --> 00:30:31,423
Point your finger...

877
00:30:31,424 --> 00:30:32,853
- while pretending not to know.
- That's right.

878
00:30:32,854 --> 00:30:34,924
If you find both of them, will you do this?

879
00:30:35,794 --> 00:30:36,864
In that case...

880
00:30:37,394 --> 00:30:38,394
(DinDin is out.)

881
00:30:38,394 --> 00:30:39,394
- Okay.
- Do this.

882
00:30:39,395 --> 00:30:40,994
- Number one is out.
- Exactly.

883
00:30:41,094 --> 00:30:42,534
Why am I saying all this?

884
00:30:42,664 --> 00:30:44,303
I can't stand to see him succeed.

885
00:30:44,304 --> 00:30:46,663
Se Yoon, to be honest, he's been getting on my nerves today.

886
00:30:46,664 --> 00:30:49,004
- Right.
- When we were playing water guns...

887
00:30:49,104 --> 00:30:50,204
He was terrible.

888
00:30:50,504 --> 00:30:52,404
(He was very harsh.)

889
00:30:53,244 --> 00:30:55,373
(Spraying his water gun everywhere...)

890
00:30:55,374 --> 00:30:57,284
(and insulting Jong Min about his age)

891
00:30:57,784 --> 00:30:59,944
(He really looked down on him.)

892
00:31:00,084 --> 00:31:01,153
Because of that one mistake...

893
00:31:01,154 --> 00:31:03,283
- What did I do to deserve that?
- I agree.

894
00:31:03,284 --> 00:31:04,783
We were just playing a game.

895
00:31:04,784 --> 00:31:07,254
For me, it was when we were doing the jump rope.

896
00:31:08,424 --> 00:31:11,024
(He didn't tolerate mistakes.)

897
00:31:11,424 --> 00:31:13,933
(Looking down on others...)

898
00:31:13,934 --> 00:31:15,994
(and acting high and mighty)

899
00:31:16,394 --> 00:31:18,154
- He couldn't understand me at all.
- Right.

900
00:31:18,334 --> 00:31:20,933
- He treated everyone like that.
- He really did.

901
00:31:20,934 --> 00:31:22,773
- We treat him with love, - Exactly.

902
00:31:22,774 --> 00:31:23,803
But he totally disrespects us.

903
00:31:23,804 --> 00:31:25,773
"I played against KAIST students."

904
00:31:25,774 --> 00:31:27,094
- He bragged about that.
- Right.

905
00:31:27,344 --> 00:31:29,614
- Suddenly, I feel so furious.
- It's infuriating.

906
00:31:30,244 --> 00:31:31,743
Let's do this. In my opinion...

907
00:31:31,744 --> 00:31:34,183
- The four of us will be a team.
- Yes.

908
00:31:34,184 --> 00:31:35,253
- Let's not betray each other.
- No.

909
00:31:35,254 --> 00:31:36,713
After eliminating DinDin first,

910
00:31:36,714 --> 00:31:38,153
- we'll fight against each other.
- Then we'll fight.

911
00:31:38,154 --> 00:31:39,923
- The four of us will play normally.
- Okay.

912
00:31:39,924 --> 00:31:42,254
- It can't be helped. Let's do it.
- Okay.

913
00:31:42,524 --> 00:31:44,394
- Se Yoon.
- Joon.

914
00:31:44,764 --> 00:31:45,893
- Jong Min.
- Seon Ho.

915
00:31:45,894 --> 00:31:47,733
- Who are we?
- 2 Days 1 Night.

916
00:31:47,734 --> 00:31:49,494
(Oath of brotherhood)

917
00:31:50,604 --> 00:31:52,664
- All right. Let's try it.
- Let's do it.

918
00:31:52,864 --> 00:31:55,534
(DinDin goes to the mission location without a clue.)

919
00:31:55,634 --> 00:31:56,804
One moment, please.

920
00:31:57,674 --> 00:31:59,643
(Why are you calling me?)

921
00:31:59,644 --> 00:32:00,673
DinDin.

922
00:32:00,674 --> 00:32:03,444
Inside, you'll find two Yakult bottles with your name on it...

923
00:32:03,814 --> 00:32:06,243
and ten bottles without any name.

924
00:32:06,244 --> 00:32:09,314
(Yakult bottles without any name)

925
00:32:09,884 --> 00:32:13,224
(2 Yakult bottles with his name)

926
00:32:13,554 --> 00:32:15,853
(10 fake Yakult bottles without any name)

927
00:32:15,854 --> 00:32:18,324
Bottles in the basket without any name.

928
00:32:18,894 --> 00:32:20,493
Hide them creatively...

929
00:32:20,494 --> 00:32:22,564
to confuse other members.

930
00:32:22,664 --> 00:32:25,304
I see. Okay.

931
00:32:25,934 --> 00:32:27,303
Please go in.

932
00:32:27,304 --> 00:32:28,703
I have to hide ten bottles?

933
00:32:28,704 --> 00:32:31,944
(The key is how well he uses deception.)

934
00:32:32,444 --> 00:32:36,644
(How will DinDin use the fake ones?)

935
00:32:37,514 --> 00:32:38,784
I'll start with one.

936
00:32:39,244 --> 00:32:41,013
(Small room)

937
00:32:41,014 --> 00:32:43,053
I'll put one of these here. It's fake.

938
00:32:43,054 --> 00:32:44,823
(Hiding a fake where it's easy to spot)

939
00:32:44,824 --> 00:32:47,954
Since it's very noticeable, they'll be excited to open it.

940
00:32:48,394 --> 00:32:50,264
Someone like Joon would open it.

941
00:32:50,724 --> 00:32:53,833
(Disrespecting even while hiding)

942
00:32:53,834 --> 00:32:54,834
(Front yard)

943
00:32:54,835 --> 00:32:57,203
Can't I put the fake ones like welcome drinks?

944
00:32:57,204 --> 00:32:58,763
(Front yard)

945
00:32:58,764 --> 00:32:59,963
Like welcome drinks.

946
00:32:59,964 --> 00:33:02,103
(Won't they get duped by a welcome drink?)

947
00:33:02,104 --> 00:33:06,003
(TV room)

948
00:33:06,004 --> 00:33:07,043
It's a fake.

949
00:33:07,044 --> 00:33:09,274
(Hiding only the fakes ones in the TV room)

950
00:33:09,414 --> 00:33:10,444
Hold on.

951
00:33:11,144 --> 00:33:12,214
Hold on.

952
00:33:12,544 --> 00:33:13,884
I put one fake in here.

953
00:33:14,414 --> 00:33:16,814
I'll put the real one here.

954
00:33:17,054 --> 00:33:18,523
(Hiding the real under a fake)

955
00:33:18,524 --> 00:33:19,653
I'll make it stand.

956
00:33:19,654 --> 00:33:21,824
(Hiding the real under a fake)

957
00:33:21,994 --> 00:33:23,923
Okay, it's real.

958
00:33:23,924 --> 00:33:25,700
(As always, he's the master of clever tricks.)

959
00:33:25,724 --> 00:33:27,764
When they find this, they'd leave with excitement.

960
00:33:28,294 --> 00:33:29,533
They'll notice that it's fake. Okay.

961
00:33:29,534 --> 00:33:31,064
(The real bottle is here.)

962
00:33:31,434 --> 00:33:33,604
(He made good use of deception.)

963
00:33:34,074 --> 00:33:36,233
(DinDin finishes hiding his bottles.)

964
00:33:36,234 --> 00:33:39,304
(Location for the other one is a secret.)

965
00:33:39,944 --> 00:33:41,244
Okay.

966
00:33:42,514 --> 00:33:43,543
- Hey.
- What's the matter?

967
00:33:43,544 --> 00:33:44,843
- What took you so long?
- I know.

968
00:33:44,844 --> 00:33:46,084
- The next member.
- Who is it?

969
00:33:46,514 --> 00:33:47,853
Please start right away.

970
00:33:47,854 --> 00:33:48,953
Five minutes isn't enough.

971
00:33:48,954 --> 00:33:50,213
- I'll be back soon.
- Okay.

972
00:33:50,214 --> 00:33:51,323
Otherwise, it'll take too long.

973
00:33:51,324 --> 00:33:52,823
- I'll be back.
- Go.

974
00:33:52,824 --> 00:33:54,893
- See you in a bit, Se Yoon.
- Good luck.

975
00:33:54,894 --> 00:33:56,023
Come back quickly.

976
00:33:56,024 --> 00:33:57,624
(Don't worry. We won't betray you.)

977
00:33:58,364 --> 00:33:59,763
(Without worrying about being betrayed, )

978
00:33:59,764 --> 00:34:01,364
(he goes to hide Yakult bottles.)

979
00:34:01,594 --> 00:34:04,763
You'll see that the rules are different from what we heard.

980
00:34:04,764 --> 00:34:06,434
Really? Is there a notice?

981
00:34:06,904 --> 00:34:08,233
- What?
- Is there a notice?

982
00:34:08,234 --> 00:34:09,910
- You'll see a notice over there.
- Really?

983
00:34:09,934 --> 00:34:11,903
Since you've played against KAIST students,

984
00:34:11,904 --> 00:34:13,850
- I'm sure that you did well.
- It was easy for me.

985
00:34:13,874 --> 00:34:16,043
- I see.
- That was expected.

986
00:34:16,044 --> 00:34:18,044
As soon as I went in,

987
00:34:18,184 --> 00:34:20,144
- I took a look around.
- And you figured it out?

988
00:34:21,184 --> 00:34:22,854
I understood what kind of game it was.

989
00:34:23,114 --> 00:34:25,753
I pictured the layout of the area in my head.

990
00:34:25,754 --> 00:34:27,923
- I knew what places to hide them.
- You're impressive.

991
00:34:27,924 --> 00:34:29,224
What do you think we'll do?

992
00:34:30,324 --> 00:34:31,564
You'd probably do this.

993
00:34:32,424 --> 00:34:33,624
"Where should I hide them?"

994
00:34:34,094 --> 00:34:36,893
"Can I hide them here? No one will find them here."

995
00:34:36,894 --> 00:34:38,014
(Unlike me, you'll be lost.)

996
00:34:38,364 --> 00:34:39,710
- Goodness.
- He's probably right.

997
00:34:39,734 --> 00:34:41,673
What should we do?

998
00:34:41,674 --> 00:34:42,703
We would probably be lost.

999
00:34:42,704 --> 00:34:44,424
(We'll make you regret what you just said.)

1000
00:34:44,504 --> 00:34:45,744
What should I do?

1001
00:34:46,344 --> 00:34:47,513
(Despite his vow for revenge, )

1002
00:34:47,514 --> 00:34:48,673
(he's actually very lost.)

1003
00:34:48,674 --> 00:34:50,843
(Side yard)

1004
00:34:50,844 --> 00:34:52,613
- These are all fake.
- Okay.

1005
00:34:52,614 --> 00:34:54,974
So that they can drink all of them and be stuffed to death.

1006
00:34:55,414 --> 00:34:56,553
Stuff yourselves to death.

1007
00:34:56,554 --> 00:34:59,053
(His strategy is to hide fake ones in the same place.)

1008
00:34:59,054 --> 00:35:00,154
That's right.

1009
00:35:00,654 --> 00:35:02,954
I'll hide the two with my name on it.

1010
00:35:04,724 --> 00:35:05,864
The jangdokdae.

1011
00:35:06,624 --> 00:35:08,894
(Jangdokdae looks like a good place to hide.)

1012
00:35:09,194 --> 00:35:11,504
(Did he stop in the bushes nearby?)

1013
00:35:14,934 --> 00:35:17,644
(Covering them with the grass)

1014
00:35:18,004 --> 00:35:20,644
(Try to find Yakult bottles.)

1015
00:35:21,074 --> 00:35:22,914
Okay. Here's one.

1016
